Package mb.pso.issuesystem.entity

Class Issue

java.lang.Object
mb.pso.issuesystem.entity.Issue
@Entity public class Issue extends Object
Represents an issue or complaint raised by a client in the system. The Issue class stores detailed information about an issue, including its status, description, related documents, assigned employees, feedback, and attached files. It also maintains relationships with other entities, such as the client who raised the issue, the type of issue, the subject matter, and any related communications.
